UseBB Development Version Upgrading
-----------------------------------

Current version: 0.4.1

Notes:
	- Install and upgrade scripts now recognize the database table
	prefix setting!
	- German translation has been removed from the package!

* Upgrading from 0.4:
	Just reupload all (newer) files. No database changes.

* Upgrading from 0.3.x:
	Run install/upgrade-0-3.php in your web browser.

* Upgrading from 0.2.3(a):
	Run install/upgrade-0-2-3.php in your web browser.

* Upgrading from 0.2.2 or earlier:
	First upgrade to 0.2.3a, then run install/upgrade-0-2-3.php.
